This is the first task in building a Smart Daily Report Email System. The AiAnalysisService will be used by:
1. MailController::sendDecr (Task 2) for email AI analysis (blocking mode)
2. TransferRequestService::transfer (Task 3) for SSE streaming AI analysis

The project is at D:\project\info-gitlab\oa\oa-core (Laravel 9, PHP 8.1).

Existing services in this project use a `ServiceTrait` that provides a static `app()` method:
```php
trait ServiceTrait {
    public static function app(array $params = []): self {
        return app(static::class, $params);
    }
}
```

